name: John Cena's Sexy Holiday Surprise!
description:
It's Christmas time with your favorite, coincidentally identical looking boys! Can Fucco-san get a present in time to save Xmas?

A very, very, very, very, VERY, short story that teaches you love, loyalty, peace and respect!

* No decisions!
* New Cenas!
* Funny moment(s)!
* Teaches you the true meaning of Xmas*!

*May or may not teach you the true meaning of Christmas
